 When you discover and awaken them, they will help you in return. These spirits can teach you new recipes, empower your base, or even imbue your ships with magic. And Ancient guardians still stand guard over powerful Elder spirits - triumph over them to prove your might and inherit their magic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686630/extras/Awaken_Spirits.gif?t=1736892377\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686630/extras/VigorDivider.png?t=1736892377\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BUILD THE ULTIMATE ISLAND BASE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build growing island settlements as you gather resources, craft new tools, and customize your buildings with an expressive construction system. Bring your base to life by awakening spirits that teach you recipes and empower your crafting stations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686630/extras/Build_Island_Base.gif?t=1736892377\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686630/extras/EnduranceDivider.png?t=1736892377\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VOYAGE ALONE OR WITH FRIENDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Voyagers is a great solo experience and even better with friends! Play with up to 10 people on a server, add new players any time and contribute through different roles. Whether you like to adventure, craft, fight, or build, every choice helps your group progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686630/extras/Great_With_Friends.gif?t=1736892377\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686630/extras/FlameDivider.png?t=1736892377\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">COMING TO EARLY ACCESS IN 2025</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a collaborative adventure with us\u2014help shape the destiny of Voyagers of Nera!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Player feedback will help make sure we\u2019re nailing our vision for the game and gives you a chance to be an integral part of our game's evolution. Add <strong>Voyagers of Nera to your wishlist</strong> to be the first to know when it\u2019s time to set sail into Early Access.</p>","developers":["Treehouse Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2686630/header.jpg?t=1736892377","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257078616,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257078616/movie480.mp4?t=1733343661","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257078616/movie_max.mp4?t=1733343661"},"name":"Voyagers of Nera 2024 Demo Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257078616/e8da02d77fcc2e6b99dcfa2d1284db932e9bba2e/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1733343661","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257078616/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1733343661","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257078616/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1733343661"}},{"highlight":false,"id":256985562,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256985562/movie480.mp4?t=1701881329","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/2569